WEBVTT

00:01:58.000 --> 00:02:00.018
They're questioning authority.

00:02:00.042 --> 00:02:02.518
But now, I'm the man.

00:02:02.542 --> 00:02:04.393
(Laughter)

00:02:04.417 --> 00:02:05.958
I'm the corporate suit.

00:02:07.042 --> 00:02:09.375
I'm the one representing authority.

00:02:10.250 --> 00:02:12.059
And this new thing was emerging

00:02:12.083 --> 00:02:14.434
called corporate social responsibility,

00:02:14.458 --> 00:02:16.934
later corporate sustainability,

00:02:16.958 --> 00:02:19.958
and now I had a chance
to make a difference.

00:02:21.042 --> 00:02:22.976
So the beginning of this journey

00:02:23.000 --> 00:02:26.434
started when McDonald's agreed
to a partnership

00:02:26.458 --> 00:02:28.768
with the Environmental Defense Fund.

00:02:28.792 --> 00:02:30.309
They were an NGO